   King Juan Carlos and Queen Sophia
of Spain took off for Hawaii on Wednesday after being briefly
delayed here by fog.
   The couple spent Wednesday touring Massey University in
Palmerston North, before flying to Auckland to board a Spanish air
force jet for Hawaii. They spent three days in New Zealand after
