and sings about drugs, gangs and other problems facing young people.
   The contest is part of a promotion for an upcoming comic strip
based on a ``Little Old Lady From Pasadena'' character.
   Ms. Smallwood, who also sings gospel, won a car, cameras,
chicken sandwiches from a fast-food chain and a trip to the
national finals in Honolulu in November.
