<HEAD>Swedish Student Dies In Fall In China</HEAD>
<DATELINE>HONG KONG (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A 25-year-old Swedish student died of internal
bleeding after he accidentally fell from the fourth floor of a
university building following a night of drinking, the China News
