<HEAD>Singer To Receive High School Diploma</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: Subs 2nd graf to CORRECT to Queens, sted Staten Island.</NOTE>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   When the Class of '88 at Richmond Hill High
School receives diplomas next week, they'll be joined by an unusual
