<1ST_LINE>u f PM-WallStreet10am     06-22 0204</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>PM-Wall Street 10am,0215</2ND_LINE>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Stock prices surged this morning in active
trading, bolstered by the momentum of a late rally in the previous
session and a strengthened dollar overseas.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials jumped 34.68 points to
